    <p>You know how you might watch a new release by streaming it on Amazon?  Or if you have prime, watch a free movie or TV show?  Our Chrome web browser extension plugs into you playback, so when you watch them on amazon, it skips the bad parts, the stuff you don't want!  Family friendly!  This allows you to kick back and relax and gives you power to control what you view.  *Compatible with Amazon and Youtube on desktop chrome browser.</p>

    <div class="mid-bar">
        <h4>Our latest additions you can watch filtered:</h4>
    </div>

    <div class="grid-x grid-padding-x small-up-3 medium-up-5 large-up-8">
      <% most_recent.each_with_index { |movie, idx| %>
        <div class="cell <%= idx > 4 ? "show-for-large" : idx > 2 ? "show-for-medium" : "" %>">
          <% box_style = "" %>
          <%= want_name = false; render "views/_box_movie_nik.ecr" %> 
        </div>
     <% } %>
    </div>
    <div class="mid-bar">
        <h4>A sample of a few more random movies from our library you can watch filtered</h4>
    </div>

    <div class="grid-x grid-padding-x small-up-3 medium-up-5 large-up-8">
      <% all_urls_done.shuffle.last(4).each_with_index { |movie, idx| %>
        <div class="cell <%= idx > 4 ? "show-for-large" : idx > 2 ? "show-for-medium" : "" %>">
          <% box_style = "" %>
          <%= want_name = false; render "views/_box_movie_nik.ecr" %> 
        </div>
     <% } %>
